survival-oriented emotions,

00:01:52.750 --> 00:01:55.170 align:middle line:84%
emotions or energy
in motion, are

00:01:55.170 --> 00:01:58.920 align:middle line:84%
low-frequency or
low-energy emotions.

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:00.800 align:middle line:84%
They vibrate at a
slower wavelength

00:02:00.800 --> 00:02:03.760 align:middle line:84%
and, therefore, ground
us into being physical.

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:07.320 align:middle line:84%
We become denser, heavier,
and more corporeal

00:02:07.320 --> 00:02:11.200 align:middle line:84%
