Or what's up with you?

00:21:16.230 --> 00:21:18.240 align:middle line:90%
Because you're exuberant.

00:21:18.240 --> 00:21:21.580 align:middle line:84%
But if you're creating
a future, and you

00:21:21.580 --> 00:21:24.670 align:middle line:84%
move into an elegant
state of creation,

00:21:24.670 --> 00:21:27.390 align:middle line:84%
and your heart is
open-- and the research

00:21:27.390 --> 00:21:29.164 align:middle line:84%
shows that the field
around the body,

00:21:29.164 --> 00:21:30.580 align:middle line:84%
when you start
opening your heart,

00:21:30.580 --> 00:21:32.100 align:middle line:90%
goes to nine meters wide.

