You become more energy
and less particle.

00:21:34.380 --> 00:21:37.210 align:middle line:84%
You're broadcasting a whole
new electromagnetic signature

00:21:37.210 --> 00:21:38.950 align:middle line:90%
into the field.

00:21:38.950 --> 00:21:42.600 align:middle line:84%
Then, you get up and you're in
a state of reverence and joy

