cursing and judging everybody.

00:21:49.330 --> 00:21:51.550 align:middle line:84%
You just returned back
to the old identity.

00:21:51.550 --> 00:21:54.020 align:middle line:84%
You have to maintain
that modified

00:21:54.020 --> 00:21:55.510 align:middle line:90%
state of mind and body.

