is really the task.

00:22:11.415 --> 00:22:12.510 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It is the task.

00:22:12.510 --> 00:22:13.880 align:middle line:84%
It's where the
commitment comes in.

00:22:13.880 --> 00:22:15.671 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: That's
where greatness is born.

00:22:15.671 --> 00:22:18.480 align:middle line:84%
So meditation, then, is to
alter your state of being

00:22:18.480 --> 00:22:22.020 align:middle line:84%
