And the one day is one lifetime.

00:22:25.840 --> 00:22:27.980 align:middle line:84%
That you are able
to master that day,

00:22:27.980 --> 00:22:31.050 align:middle line:84%
then, begins to allow you
to leave your past behind

00:22:31.050 --> 00:22:32.150 align:middle line:90%
and create a new future.

00:22:32.150 --> 00:22:34.740 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Even just
starting with an hour,

