00:23:41.950 --> 00:23:44.450 align:middle line:84%
And you brought them
together with yourself

00:23:44.450 --> 00:23:47.550 align:middle line:84%
to start looking--
well, you tell us

00:23:47.550 --> 00:23:49.450 align:middle line:84%
what you began doing in
this experimentation.

00:23:49.450 --> 00:23:51.820 align:middle line:84%
Because the results
are really fascinating.

00:23:51.820 --> 00:23:53.570 align:middle line:90%
>>DISPENZA: Sure.

00:23:53.570 --> 00:23:55.760 align:middle line:84%
When I wrote my first
book, "Evolve your Brain,"

00:23:55.760 --> 00:23:58.850 align:middle line:84%
