health conditions.

00:24:05.330 --> 00:24:07.460 align:middle line:84%
And they were treating
conventionally or

00:24:07.460 --> 00:24:08.260 align:middle line:90%
unconventionally.

00:24:08.260 --> 00:24:09.940 align:middle line:84%
And they were staying the
same or getting worse.

00:24:09.940 --> 00:24:11.497 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden,
they got better.

00:24:11.497 --> 00:24:13.080 align:middle line:84%
So I wanted to know
what the cause was

00:24:13.080 --> 00:24:14.590 align:middle line:90%
that produced that effect.

00:24:14.590 --> 00:24:18.870 align:middle line:84%
So we found four common
things that they had.

00:24:18.870 --> 00:24:20.710 align:middle line:84%
And that was what
the book was about.

00:24:20.710 --> 00:24:22.560 align:middle line:84%
And then we did
"What the Bleep."

00:24:22.560 --> 00:24:25.647 align:middle line:84%
And then, afterwards,
people start saying, well,

00:24:25.647 --> 00:24:26.980 align:middle line:90%
