00:24:28.230 --> 00:24:31.890 align:middle line:84%
So we started teaching workshops
around the world and really

00:24:31.890 --> 00:24:33.430 align:middle line:84%
teaching people the
how to process--

00:24:33.430 --> 00:24:36.120 align:middle line:84%
